{
  "_comment": "Copy this file to .claude/settings.local.json to opt into convenience permissions for your local workflow. The .local.json file is gitignored, so your personal trust decisions stay off the public default. The committed .claude/settings.json intentionally ships with a minimal defensive allowlist for public users — add here whatever you personally trust.",

